{"tid":301674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［解夢］有冇人經常發夢自殺","createTime":"2017-06-28T23:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T00:27:31.000Z","uid":8673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7c4d0f66d2443d3ecb0a7a0bb89e057685804f","tid":301674,"uid":8673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:00:55.000Z","msg":"呢排發夢，經常夢見自己同另一半嘈交，然後由一座大廈到跳落黎，死左之後變成靈魂，飛返上座大廈到，睇下另一半有冇為我難過，然後見到佢發現好多我為佢準備既野，之後佢就落淚，個夢都去到呢度就完結。<br />\n呢個夢已經係第4次了，每次都一樣結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14e4d78fec46612b32a0d84c88d323855851820","tid":301674,"uid":8673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f257880fb059c8604905b498b9685a0ceccc2ca","tid":301674,"uid":3503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:12:18.000Z","msg":"我會用跳樓個下離心力整醒自己"},{"pid":"fe96966bf4877e32bfcbd0b2a64f30589f0e63f1","tid":301674,"uid":8673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會用跳樓個下離心力整醒自己</blockquote><br />\n我改變唔到個夢，平時果啲我會知自己發緊夢，然後控制到"},{"pid":"b96056f1b5031c09d8ed7bdb669b0dc496844f5f","tid":301674,"uid":8673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca74a4f0c67f95da59b5b43ebd498608038e7d5","tid":301674,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:13:50.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"b9c215b036a091debdce1748d3ec7ef91b4877bf","tid":301674,"uid":113090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"試過唯一一次 同樓主一樣又係跳樓死咗之後變靈魂周圍行 之後突然醒咗起身睇下幾點 呀媽係呢刻突然入嚟問我做咩唔瞓 起身之後問佢做乜無啦啦入嚟佢話突然紮醒覺得不安喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n都10年前事 但而家都覺得好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b3eb9493eca70e417bb0e8d9bd0ad0089c1c8e","tid":301674,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:27:31.000Z","msg":"建議你睇下醫生，可能有夢遊症<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}